    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Track keyword rankings with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive\n\n**Pattern:** SEO Audit · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nTrack keyword rankings with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual backlinks is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Probe Endpoint A → Combine Probe Results → All Healthy? → Record Uptime Metric → Sort Pages Newest First → Guard Non-Empty url → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to seo audit without manual effort\n- Anyone automating backlinks in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "23d3fe99-3310-793b-d96f-26a8f9779d5b",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
